subject: Hello,
body:
Hello,
How are you? I hope the email meets you well. I have important information that concerns you, which I would like to share with you.
Best regards,
Andrew Bailey

subject: Re:  Hello,
body:
Hello Andrew Bailey,

I'm doing well, thank you for asking. I hope this email finds you in good health too. I'm curious to know what important information you have to share with me. Could you please provide more details? I'm open to hearing what you have to say.

Best wishes,
Dustin
